    <summaries>
      <summary>
        <versionCode>00</versionCode>
        <actionDate>2007-02-07</actionDate>
        <actionDesc>Introduced in Senate</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2007-02-26T18:19:56Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Amends the John Warner National Defense Authorization Act for Fiscal Year 2007 to repeal provisions authorizing the President to: (1) employ the Armed Forces to restore public order and enforce the law in major public emergencies; and (2) provide supplies, services, and equipment to persons affected by the situation.</p> <p>Restores previous authority of the President to use the Armed Forces to suppress situations which interfere with state or federal law.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
